1
00:00:01,270 --> 00:00:05,780
Parallel world stories usually begin like this

2
00:00:06,030 --> 00:00:07,700
...or so it is

3
00:00:08,050 --> 00:00:11,890
The merciful goddess bestows strength upon the hero.

4
00:00:11,900 --> 00:00:14,530
The Beginning Town

5
00:00:12,100 --> 00:00:14,530
And beloved by the inhabitants of the parallel world

6
00:00:14,790 --> 00:00:18,020
The hero enjoys his adventure in the company of the beautiful heroines.

7
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:21,480
I thought so.

8
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:24,710
But these are my heroines.

9
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:28,610
These are my adventures.

10
00:00:29,280 --> 00:00:32,140
To make matters worse, I suffer from such things.

11
00:00:32,930 --> 00:00:36,730
...and what I've learned since arriving in a parallel world is

12
00:00:37,420 --> 00:00:41,510
I'm unlucky when it comes to parallel universes.

13
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:45,190
My name is Misumi Makoto, and my life is a farce.

14
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:20,340
My life was ordinary.

15
00:02:20,530 --> 00:02:22,780
I have breakfast with my family in the morning.

16
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:25,160
After work, I practice shooting.

17
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:27,270
I will have dinner afterwards.

18
00:02:27,270 --> 00:02:29,640
After showering, I browse the internet and read books.

19
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:32,040
Knights of the Parallel World (Part Two)

20
00:02:30,200 --> 00:02:32,940
Oh~ My dad's new book is out!

21
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:38,050
Misumi

22
00:02:34,380 --> 00:02:37,790
It was a quiet day, like any other.

23
00:02:38,770 --> 00:02:42,700
So it's strange that I'm not sleeping in our house.

24
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,390
Where am I?

25
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:48,930
First night

26
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:48,930
Hero... Failure

27
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:48,160
...you seem calm

28
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:48,930
Who's there?

29
00:02:49,250 --> 00:02:51,870
Would you believe me if I said I am a god?

30
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:52,930
No, impossible.

31
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:56,340
You are about to go to a parallel world.

32
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:58,440
Therefore, please sign your consent.

33
00:02:58,710 --> 00:03:02,230
Your sudden talk about such a topic is causing me trouble.

34
00:03:02,230 --> 00:03:05,930
That's strange. I heard you were aware of the matter.

35
00:03:05,930 --> 00:03:07,620
Please excuse me.

36
00:03:08,810 --> 00:03:12,560
My name is Tsukuyomi. The Dominator of the Night World.

37
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:17,240
I came to make you a hero and deliver you to the goddess of the parallel world.

38
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:20,260
Tsukuyomi? Do you mean as in Tsukuyomi-no-mikoto?

39
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:23,900
One of the three noble children in Japanese mythology?

40
00:03:23,900 --> 00:03:26,490
Ah, you're very knowledgeable.

41
00:03:26,810 --> 00:03:29,140
What are you doing here, Tsukuyomi-sama?

42
00:03:29,380 --> 00:03:32,040
You don't really know anything.

43
00:03:32,410 --> 00:03:36,900
First, your parents are from a parallel universe.

44
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,190
What?

45
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:40,190
!What?

46
00:03:40,190 --> 00:03:44,160
Now that I've mentioned it, I haven't met any of our relatives at all.

47
00:03:44,160 --> 00:03:45,700
But a parallel world?

48
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,880
For special reasons

49
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:52,050
Your parents signed a contract with the goddess of the parallel world
and went to Japan.

50
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:57,520
They agreed to give her the most precious thing they owned someday.

51
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:03,380
Does this mean that one of my sisters, Yukiko-Nissan or
Mari, will be taken if I don't go?

52
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,540
.actually

53
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:09,250
...I understand, I'll go. But

54
00:04:09,510 --> 00:04:12,260
Don't worry, Makoto-dono

55
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:18,070
I will take it upon myself to dispose of the
numerous products she owns that depict men's dreams!

56
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:21,740
You are God, a true God!

57
00:04:24,220 --> 00:04:26,210
The contract looks good like this.

58
00:04:26,210 --> 00:04:28,810
Is this the only message you want to send to your family?

59
00:04:28,810 --> 00:04:29,460
.Okay

60
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,320
...permission

61
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,110
What is this?

62
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:35,400
You will now give up the world you have been living in.

63
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:38,640
I will give you all the strength I can give you.

64
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:41,740
Thank you very much... Wait?

65
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:46,420
O goddess! Do you intend to take him without greeting me?

66
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:51,420
Oh, Makoto-dono, the goddess you're about to meet
. She has a lot of problems.

67
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:54,690
But I want you to be as patient as possible.

68
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,700
Good!

69
00:04:56,700 --> 00:05:01,690
Since this is your wish, I will even accept a goddess
... I have never heard of before.

70
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:06,190
The light is bright!

71
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:08,790
What? Did you arrive?

72
00:05:08,790 --> 00:05:12,610
...Old Tsukuyomi's strength must have weakened

73
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:14,980
A- The goddess?

74
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:20,130
In fact, demons and spirits in this
world began to do as they pleased.

75
00:05:20,130 --> 00:05:22,970
My humans are in a big predicament.

76
00:05:23,250 --> 00:05:25,900
That's why I thought of calling you to help them.

77
00:05:28,730 --> 00:05:31,650
Are you really their son?

78
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:33,790
You are extremely ugly!

79
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:38,440
To clarify: This is a reference to the story of the ugly duckling that became a swan.

80
00:05:34,260 --> 00:05:36,220
The probability of becoming a swan is zero.

81
00:05:36,220 --> 00:05:38,440
From which ugly duckling's nest did you come?

82
00:05:38,780 --> 00:05:40,900
However, there will be a period of inactivity for the summons.

83
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,960
Why don't you hurry up and disappear from my sight?

84
00:05:42,960 --> 00:05:44,740
Your very presence is disgusting and annoying.

85
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,350
But you're the one who summoned me!

86
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:50,890
Oh my! Even your voice is ugly!

87
00:05:50,890 --> 00:05:54,760
I have already found other heroes for my world

88
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:58,330
So stay at the end of my world and don't defile it with your filth.

89
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,440
What?

90
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:02,910
I don't like the idea of ​​giving you any power.

91
00:06:03,220 --> 00:06:09,650
But I will give you the ability to understand, speak, read
, and write languages ​​other than human language.

92
00:06:09,650 --> 00:06:11,390
What a headache!

93
00:06:13,490 --> 00:06:17,630
Enjoy your lowly life with the orcs and goblins

94
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:22,110
But beware of spreading your ugly offspring among my people!

95
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,820
Now get out!

96
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:27,120
I wonder if the fall will kill him.

97
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,110
I can't stand the thought of him coming back again!

98
00:06:30,110 --> 00:06:33,240
You must be joking!

99
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,450
Are you treating me like a cockroach?

100
00:06:35,450 --> 00:06:37,260
Damn you!

101
00:06:38,400 --> 00:06:39,340
!Makoto-dono

102
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:41,120
Tsukuyomi-sama!

103
00:06:42,200 --> 00:06:45,260
It never occurred to me that the goddess could go this far.

104
00:06:45,260 --> 00:06:48,580
Well, you'll be fine even if you fall from this height.

105
00:06:48,580 --> 00:06:49,140
What?

106
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:55,170
The world you lived in was harsh and desolate
, and far removed from our protection.

107
00:06:55,170 --> 00:06:59,350
Your magical and physical strength were under a heavy burden.

108
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:04,020
You are supposed to be strong in this world by freeing yourself
from that burden.

109
00:07:04,020 --> 00:07:06,110
What a fitting interpretation!

110
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:09,860
But you will die when your time comes. A warning has been given.

111
00:07:10,740 --> 00:07:11,480
What?

112
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,210
...your body, Tsukuyomi-sama

113
00:07:14,210 --> 00:07:17,120
This communication has drained a great deal of my energy.

114
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:20,740
I will now have to sleep for centuries.

115
00:07:21,020 --> 00:07:22,470
...not possible

116
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:27,450
The goddess herself has stripped you of your role as a hero.

117
00:07:27,450 --> 00:07:29,010
There is no longer a need for reservations.

118
00:07:29,450 --> 00:07:34,330
...in my name, Tsukuyomi, i.e., Misumi Makoto

119
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:37,680
I give you freedom in your new world!

120
00:07:38,350 --> 00:07:42,130
I hope we meet again in the cycle of your rebirth.

121
00:07:45,300 --> 00:07:46,680
...Tsukuyomi-sama

122
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,390
!Okay

123
00:08:00,660 --> 00:08:05,070
...Three days have passed since I fell to this ground

124
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:08,180
And she began walking towards that towering mountain.

125
00:08:09,090 --> 00:08:12,280
I didn't encounter any humans, animals, or even anything edible.

126
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:17,680
Can I move after 3 days
without eating because I am a superhuman?

127
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:21,280
Talking to myself is pointless and achieves nothing.

128
00:08:23,690 --> 00:08:25,210
Three days have passed, then?

129
00:08:25,210 --> 00:08:28,690
Only my own voice, the sound of my footsteps, and the wind are all I hear.

130
00:08:28,690 --> 00:08:32,700
Normally, some kind of event would have happened before
I reached this stage.

131
00:08:36,190 --> 00:08:37,350
I feel lonely.

132
00:08:39,130 --> 00:08:41,310
Someone please help me.

133
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:44,450
Where is it coming from? Where did this sound come from?

134
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,960
Someone please help me!

135
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,720
From here!

136
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:53,420
Someone please help me!

137
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:55,410
Yes, with pleasure!

138
00:08:56,210 --> 00:08:56,920
Huh?

139
00:08:57,170 --> 00:08:58,780
A dog with two heads?

140
00:08:59,050 --> 00:09:01,100
And a pig wearing clothes?

141
00:09:01,730 --> 00:09:05,110
It doesn't matter! This is better than being alone.

142
00:09:05,110 --> 00:09:07,760
Who are you?

143
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:11,270
Hello! I'm a human and my name is Makoto.

144
00:09:11,530 --> 00:09:13,400
What?! It's so fast!

145
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,960
I'm delighted to meet you!

146
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,440
Huh?

147
00:09:27,330 --> 00:09:28,830
...disgusting

148
00:09:30,810 --> 00:09:32,990
...I did it

149
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:38,080
...H- Good

150
00:09:38,780 --> 00:09:40,230
I'm happy to meet you.

151
00:09:40,230 --> 00:09:43,270
What? Why is he talking to a human being?

152
00:09:43,490 --> 00:09:45,660
Why am I talking to a pig?

153
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:48,020
A- Anyway, everything is fine.

154
00:09:48,020 --> 00:09:50,080
I am a kind and gentle person.

155
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,690
You are not gentle at all.

156
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:56,020
But I saved you, didn't I?

157
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:58,200
In other words, I am your ally.

158
00:09:58,530 --> 00:09:59,780
Escape: 1

159
00:09:58,530 --> 00:09:59,780
Okay

160
00:09:58,530 --> 00:09:59,780
impossible

161
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:01,030
2: Fighting

162
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:01,030
Okay

163
00:09:59,780 --> 00:10:01,030
Most impossible

164
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:03,040
3: Surrender

165
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:03,040
Okay

166
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:04,680
I understand.

167
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,040
!amazing

168
00:10:06,630 --> 00:10:09,730
In fact, I was lost for three days.

169
00:10:09,730 --> 00:10:12,090
Do you know where I should go to meet other people?

170
00:10:12,990 --> 00:10:16,050
There are no human villages nearby.

171
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:19,670
This desolate place is known as the wasteland and is located at the ends of the earth.

172
00:10:19,670 --> 00:10:23,790
That vile goddess has already thrown me to the ends of the earth.

173
00:10:24,370 --> 00:10:28,180
A. My name is Emma and I am a Hill Ork.

174
00:10:28,430 --> 00:10:30,630
Ah, my name is Makoto.

175
00:10:30,630 --> 00:10:33,960
Excuse me, but is your village near here?

176
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:40,360
No, I was on my way to the Holy Mountain.

177
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:44,420
To offer myself as a sacrifice to Shin-sama

178
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,910
The harbinger of the event appeared!

179
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:50,350
Several years ago, fog enveloped my village.

180
00:10:50,350 --> 00:10:52,530
Our crops no longer produce yields.

181
00:10:52,530 --> 00:10:56,310
The fog began to dissipate after the offerings were made.

182
00:10:56,310 --> 00:10:57,910
So you have to do this?

183
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:02,280
There is a place in front of us where you can bathe.

184
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:04,770
As a token of my gratitude for being saved from the two-headed dog

185
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:07,550
There you can relieve yourself of the burden of travel.

186
00:11:07,550 --> 00:11:10,180
She is intelligent and her behavior is excellent.

187
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,850
I would save her if I could.

188
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:13,850
Makoto-sama?

189
00:11:13,850 --> 00:11:17,100
What a fragrant scent, redolent with the aroma of flowers!

190
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:20,360
...if I had saved this young lady

191
00:11:20,810 --> 00:11:24,480
This suggests that she will become the heroine of my story!

192
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:31,340
My first meal in days

193
00:11:31,650 --> 00:11:34,650
I've heard that humans are a violent and cruel race.

194
00:11:34,650 --> 00:11:39,340
Perhaps he has subhuman blood running through his veins
; look at his appearance.

195
00:11:39,340 --> 00:11:41,750
I'm sorry for being ugly.

196
00:11:43,070 --> 00:11:45,320
Impossible! The pots are floating!

197
00:11:45,320 --> 00:11:48,520
.إنه مجرد سحر نقل نستعمله بشكل يومي

198
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:51,270
Can you use magic, Emma-san?

199
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:54,270
Huh? Can't you use it, Makoto-sama?

200
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:57,180
No, I absolutely cannot.

201
00:11:57,180 --> 00:11:59,740
Would you be willing to teach me if you don't mind?

202
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:04,010
Let's start with the basics, then.

203
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:07,550
I call upon you, O flame that forms the essence of fire.

204
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:08,710
gunshot

205
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:11,630
!amazing

206
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:18,120
This amulet is like a magic key that grants magical energy
properties or changes in its properties.

207
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:21,500
This spell is difficult to cast
, as it is not in the Orc language.

208
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,920
It seemed to me like the same language

209
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:29,080
I call upon you, O flame that forms the essence of fire.

210
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,080
gunshot

211
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,620
Wow! I did it!

212
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,180
What should I do now?

213
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:39,280
Imagine a ball of fire and throw it towards your target.

214
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:42,740
...I imagine, then? I imagine

215
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:45,670
And then... my throat!

216
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,230
!Hurrah

217
00:12:49,540 --> 00:12:51,320
Does this mean I have mastered the spell?

218
00:12:51,660 --> 00:12:54,390
I can't believe you did it so easily.

219
00:12:54,710 --> 00:12:58,260
What is your current level, Makoto-sama?

220
00:12:58,930 --> 00:13:01,450
Are there levels?

221
00:13:02,250 --> 00:13:03,470
what is going on?

222
00:13:03,470 --> 00:13:05,140
It measures his level

223
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,020
Let's see

224
00:13:06,300 --> 00:13:10,280
Your level is undoubtedly 200... No, probably 300.

225
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:12,160
Please hold this paper tightly.

226
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:13,310
Okay

227
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:16,940
What level is this?

228
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,310
...good

229
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:20,700
Level 1

230
00:13:21,410 --> 00:13:22,660
one?

231
00:13:24,370 --> 00:13:28,660
If you wish, shall I teach you other incantations?

232
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:31,350
Yes, thank you.

233
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:37,110
Makoto-sama?

234
00:13:38,790 --> 00:13:40,370
Makoto-sama?

235
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:42,970
To dear Emma-san

236
00:13:43,540 --> 00:13:44,960
Thank you so much for what you did yesterday.

237
00:13:45,280 --> 00:13:49,630
I will take the scroll of spells and equipment you gave me.

238
00:13:49,630 --> 00:13:54,040
This isn't a thank you, but I'll sort this out with
Shin-sama somehow.

239
00:13:54,040 --> 00:13:55,550
.Revelation

240
00:13:56,830 --> 00:13:59,720
I was able to read the scroll of incantations and write a letter.

241
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:02,080
It must be the power of that vile goddess.

242
00:14:03,800 --> 00:14:09,060
If I disappear after Shin's defeat
, I'll be able to skip the wedding event.

243
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:11,600
I would like to resolve this matter through dialogue if possible.

244
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:15,260
But perhaps I should train in case I have to fight.

245
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:17,950
gunshot

246
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:23,100
Good, I can do this without saying the incantation.

247
00:14:23,100 --> 00:14:26,950
If I could change the form of
magical energy, I would try this.

248
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,970
That thing serves as a suitable target.

249
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,860
Good. You succeeded.

250
00:14:41,300 --> 00:14:42,510
What?

251
00:14:44,540 --> 00:14:46,090
.Unfortunately

252
00:14:49,830 --> 00:14:51,410
!I'm sorry

253
00:14:51,780 --> 00:14:55,490
Are you cooperating with the Orcs?

254
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:59,530
They look evil no matter how I look at them.

255
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:06,250
We were planning to subdue the Orcs using the name Shin.

256
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:09,300
I rushed things in the end.

257
00:15:09,300 --> 00:15:11,510
It destroyed his lair.

258
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:15,300
Shin's anger will become a reality.

259
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:18,980
This is what you deserve.

260
00:15:19,930 --> 00:15:20,970
clouds?

261
00:15:21,430 --> 00:15:23,030
No, is it fog?

262
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:36,990
According to traditional accounts, Shen Mahar
...a giant capable of creating mirages

263
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:43,210
But what is normal for me does not apply to this world.

264
00:15:46,330 --> 00:15:48,200
Does he attack by surprise?

265
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:54,430
It passed peacefully. I'm alive.

266
00:15:57,110 --> 00:15:58,660
The fog is preventing me from seeing.

267
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:01,430
This fog is also not ordinary.

268
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:12,070
I avoided it.

269
00:16:12,070 --> 00:16:13,740
Was it my instinct? No

270
00:16:21,690 --> 00:16:27,130
Is this the power that Tsukuyomi-sama gave me?

271
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:30,340
The gunshot, then?

272
00:16:30,740 --> 00:16:34,390
Receiving a blow with this spell will not bring me
any pain or harm whatsoever.

273
00:16:37,650 --> 00:16:42,180
A wound? Was I wounded? Even though I am immune to fire?

274
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:43,860
...punch

275
00:16:44,380 --> 00:16:46,320
!directly

276
00:16:46,320 --> 00:16:48,020
...followed

277
00:16:48,020 --> 00:16:49,520
A punch with the back of the hand!

278
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,510
Who is this creature?

279
00:16:52,510 --> 00:16:55,040
I'm supposed to be invincible.

280
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:57,510
...And now, the conclusion

281
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:59,950
The rising frog's jump punch!

282
00:17:00,770 --> 00:17:03,090
Shame on you

283
00:17:05,570 --> 00:17:07,840
Shame on you!

284
00:17:08,870 --> 00:17:10,570
What-what is going on?

285
00:17:11,180 --> 00:17:12,900
The matter is settled.

286
00:17:13,100 --> 00:17:17,930
You will drown in the bliss of my memories
, and meet your end.

287
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:24,240
I'm doing well.

288
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,350
a) Excuse me

289
00:17:27,410 --> 00:17:30,350
Oh~ Hasegawa. What's wrong?

290
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:33,110
...H- Good

291
00:17:33,110 --> 00:17:34,870
Side braid

292
00:17:34,870 --> 00:17:38,620
She's been styling her hair like this ever since I told her
it suited her.

293
00:17:38,980 --> 00:17:41,310
Doesn't it give her a headache?

294
00:17:41,310 --> 00:17:42,600
Misumi-senpai!

295
00:17:43,370 --> 00:17:45,360
I have always looked forward to you

296
00:17:45,360 --> 00:17:49,040
I love you! Will you go out with me?

297
00:17:49,990 --> 00:17:51,050
What?

298
00:17:52,360 --> 00:17:55,050
To be honest, my appearance isn't great.

299
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:58,590
I love school, but I'm not exceptionally smart.

300
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:00,090
...and on top of that

301
00:18:01,380 --> 00:18:03,050
Senpai?

302
00:18:03,210 --> 00:18:05,530
No, no! Wait!

303
00:18:05,790 --> 00:18:08,400
This is very surprising.

304
00:18:10,930 --> 00:18:11,690
Wait!

305
00:18:12,710 --> 00:18:14,290
Don't cry, Hasegawa.

306
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:16,940
So, we can try this for a while.

307
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:19,820
And then you can fall in love with me!

308
00:18:19,820 --> 00:18:21,410
!any?

309
00:18:21,410 --> 00:18:22,890
Is this impossible?

310
00:18:22,890 --> 00:18:25,410
No, I can't refuse.

311
00:18:25,690 --> 00:18:29,920
Whoa, then, he's a visitor from another world.

312
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:32,670
...Huh? This memory

313
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:35,660
What is this? I've never seen anything like it before.

314
00:18:35,860 --> 00:18:38,950
I want to ask him about this directly and get him to tell me about it.

315
00:18:39,330 --> 00:18:43,840
When I saw you draw your bow, I couldn't take my eyes off you.

316
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:47,170
That's why I joined the shooting club.

317
00:18:47,810 --> 00:18:48,780
Senpai?

318
00:18:49,540 --> 00:18:52,700
- I understand, thank you Hasegawa.

319
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:54,620
Please call me by my name!

320
00:18:54,980 --> 00:18:57,370
Call me No-ko-mi

321
00:18:57,370 --> 00:19:00,000
Yes, but we are currently

322
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:03,500
Let's spend lots of time together
during the summer vacation, Senpai.

323
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:07,000
A- Yes, I'm looking forward to this.

324
00:19:07,690 --> 00:19:10,750
No, that's not true.

325
00:19:11,070 --> 00:19:12,810
...because then

326
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:16,120
I cried Hasegawa.

327
00:19:17,390 --> 00:19:21,430
I'm sorry, Hasegawa, for making you play a role
in this comedy sketch.

328
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:27,680
I began to understand the power that Tsukuyomi-sama had given me.

329
00:19:28,040 --> 00:19:34,680
I can create a hemispherical sphere around
myself and control the space within it.

330
00:19:35,370 --> 00:19:39,960
For example, I can conduct research without being noticed.

331
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:42,400
I can also strengthen myself

332
00:19:43,570 --> 00:19:48,280
Thank you, Shane, for making me realize how pathetic I am.

333
00:19:49,450 --> 00:19:51,280
What a unique power!

334
00:19:51,790 --> 00:19:54,630
But I no longer harbor any animosity towards him.

335
00:19:59,050 --> 00:20:01,220
Please control your anger.

336
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:03,650
Although it was merely an illusion reflecting your hidden desire

337
00:20:03,650 --> 00:20:07,230
I am so sorry for making you suffer these feelings.

338
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:10,220
Was that my deepest desire?

339
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:14,320
Dear visitor from the parallel world, my name is Shin.

340
00:20:14,320 --> 00:20:17,150
I consider myself an invincible creature because I am a great dragon.

341
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:19,880
My name is Misumi Makoto.

342
00:20:19,880 --> 00:20:22,120
As you mentioned before, I am a visitor from a parallel universe.

343
00:20:22,340 --> 00:20:25,570
Wouldn't you like to make a contract with me, Makoto-dono?

344
00:20:25,570 --> 00:20:26,620
What?

345
00:20:26,810 --> 00:20:29,890
The knot is a special type of magic that grants several benefits.

346
00:20:29,890 --> 00:20:32,300
When the two parties divide it amongst themselves

347
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:36,630
The strength of both sides can be increased based on their relative strength.

348
00:20:36,870 --> 00:20:37,860
In other words?

349
00:20:37,860 --> 00:20:41,040
This means I will become your companion, Makoto-dono.

350
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:42,960
I promise you my hope will not be disappointed.

351
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:47,990
I am deeply interested in your memories, Makoto-dono.

352
00:20:47,990 --> 00:20:49,380
I look forward to your approval.

353
00:20:49,560 --> 00:20:52,530
How much of my memories did I see?

354
00:20:52,530 --> 00:20:53,900
And what secrets did you discover?

355
00:20:54,970 --> 00:20:59,120
I'm wondering about this. I'm certain the contract will benefit us both.

356
00:20:59,420 --> 00:21:00,890
...you conspirator

357
00:21:01,580 --> 00:21:04,330
Okay! I look forward to our future days.

358
00:21:04,330 --> 00:21:06,140
Like you, I hope our relationship will last for years to come.

359
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:10,490
Let's perform the ritual of concluding the contract.

360
00:21:11,570 --> 00:21:14,250
We will begin with the 50:50 charter.

361
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:17,510
Did he surpass me in strength?

362
00:21:17,740 --> 00:21:20,350
Let's try 70:30 then.

363
00:21:20,950 --> 00:21:22,820
It is absolutely unique!

364
00:21:22,820 --> 00:21:26,000
Okay, let's try 80:20!

365
00:21:27,810 --> 00:21:30,220
We are finally getting closer to the right balance.

366
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:32,820
Although I am effectively his slave

367
00:21:34,730 --> 00:21:37,350
...that doesn't matter, this person

368
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:42,810
No, I'm looking forward to what my master will do in the future.

369
00:21:43,670 --> 00:21:49,540
It seems to me that the time I will spend with
my master will be the greatest time of my life.

370
00:21:50,870 --> 00:21:55,320
Once again, I look forward to our future together, Mr. Makoto-sama.

371
00:21:55,320 --> 00:21:57,780
A dignified beauty in Japanese clothing?

372
00:21:57,780 --> 00:22:00,040
I prefer you to call me Samurai

373
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:02,950
You are closer to being a hero than a heroine.

374
00:23:36,910 --> 00:23:39,840
"The Second Night: The Black Doomsday Spider"

375
00:23:37,100 --> 00:23:39,970
Next episode

376
00:23:38,060 --> 00:23:39,970
Black disaster spider

